**Overview**

This dashboard provides an in-depth analysis of MongoDB Atlas database logs, tracking severity levels, log messages by host, and error distributions. It visualizes trends in warnings, errors, and fatal messages over time while categorizing issues by components such as network, access, and geo-related events. By monitoring these insights, users can proactively address potential issues, improve database reliability, and enhance overall system performance.
